{"title":"This Focus Izalco Max with dual power meter pedals and a front derailleur weighs just 5.2kg","link":"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/focus-izalco-max-national-hill-climb-championships-2023","date":1699024895000,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/focus-izalco-max-national-hill-climb-championships-2023\">This Focus Izalco Max with dual power meter pedals and a front derailleur weighs just 5.2kg</a></p>\n\n<p>For many, hill climbs are about building the craziest, lightest bike possible and there are a few standard modifications that they’ll use. This Focus Izalco Max is a prime example of the classic sawn-off drop bar cockpit, but that’s where its normalness ends. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>While <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/best-power-meters-an-aid-to-better-training\" target=\"_blank\">power meters</a> are relatively common now, Kit Buchanan chose to fit his steed with dual <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/reviews/favero-assioma-duo-shi-power-pedals-review\" target=\"_blank\">Favero Assioma pedals</a>. Not only that but he also opted for a 2× drivetrain, favouring a wider ratio rather than eschewing the front derailleur and second chainring. </p>\n\n\n<div>\r\n                <div>\r\n                   <div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <h4><span>Related Posts</span></h4>\r\n                      </div>\r\n                      <div>\r\n                         <div>\r\n                            <div>\r\n                            <article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-road-cycling-tyres-the-best-tyres-for-all-occasions\">Best road bike tyres 2023: 10 of the best tyres for all occasions</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/best-road-bike\">Best road bikes: Best bikes from under £1,000 to over £10,000</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article><article>\r\n                    <div>\r\n                       <h4>\r\n                          <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/buying-guides/buyers-guide-to-the-best-clipless-road-bike-pedals\">Best road bike pedals 2023</a>\r\n                       </h4>\r\n                    </div>\r\n                 </article></div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <span></span><span></span><span></span>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                        <div>\r\n                                            <div>\r\n                                                <div></div>\r\n                                            </div>\r\n                                        </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                    <div>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                        <span></span>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                    </div>\r\n                                </div>\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\r\n                        </div>\r\n                        </div>\n\n\n<p>And yet, the full build still weighed in at a grand total of 5.2kg for the National Hill Climb Championship 2023. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Perhaps it was the ultra-light Mavic Cosmic Carbone wheels, with their carbon hubs and spokes, or maybe the CNC-ed aluminium July 21 brake calipers with Alligator i-Link cable outers. Whatever it was, it put Buchanan in good stead – he came a respectable 88th out of the 275 riders in the senior male category. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Keep scrolling for close up photos of the full build.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-2-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Charlotte Head</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We appreciate the attention to detail in colour-matching not only the cable outer but also the rear light to the paintwork.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-5-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Charlotte Head</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The July 21 brake calipers feature a titanium pivot bolt and are CNC-ed from 6066-T6 aluminium.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-1-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Charlotte Head</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>A carbon hub shell and carbon spokes on the Mavic Cosmic Carbone Ultimate wheels.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-3-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Charlotte Head</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><img width=\"970\" height=\"647\" src=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-970x647.jpg\" srcset=\"https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-970x646.jpg 970w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-300x200.jpg 300w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-768x512.jpg 768w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-1536x1024.jpg 1536w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-2048x1365.jpg 2048w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-750x500.jpg 750w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-1140x760.jpg 1140w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-465x310.jpg 465w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-620x413.jpg 620w, https://dqh479dn9vg99.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2023/11/focus_hill_climb_nationals_2023-4-350x233.jpg 350w\" /><figcaption>Charlotte Head</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Front derailleur be damned, this bike was still impressively featherweight.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Kit Buchanan’s Focus Izalco Max spec</h2>\n\n\n\n<table>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Frameset</td><td>Focus Izalco Max</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Weight</td><td>5.2kg</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Groupset</td><td>SRAM Red 11-speed mechanical</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Brakes</td><td>July 21 aluminium road calipers 6066-T6</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Crankset</td><td>SRAM Red, TA Specialites chainring 50/34</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Pedals</td><td>Favero Assioma DUO</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Wheels</td><td>Mavic Cosmic Carbone Ultimate</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n\t<td>Tyres</td><td>Veloflex front tyre, rear unknown</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk/in-depth/focus-izalco-max-national-hill-climb-championships-2023\">This Focus Izalco Max with dual power meter pedals and a front derailleur weighs just 5.2kg</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://www.cyclist.co.uk\">Cyclist</a>.</p>","author":"Charlotte Head &#124; Tech Writer","siteTitle":"Cyclist.co.uk","siteHash":"561486e7070fa5351de9318ad0fa26c2a39332acba5fc7c7d1694a01d53d431e","entryHash":"b0b65c233053a607a2d458b953ce3014410b7724fa40fe209c8bc34aa1ef5ad8","category":"Cycling"}